{"tid":1886000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"截至昨日，10395人接受強制隔離  [9163香港人，1232外地人]  8749人家居檢疫","createTime":"2020-02-18T16:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T16:09:46.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f6214f925709c22a3fa1785f634b18fa0d39a3e","tid":1886000,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"截至昨日共有10395人接受強制檢疫<br />\n<br />\n政府提交立法會的文件指，截至昨日，共有10395人接受強制檢疫，包括9163名香港居民及1232名非香港居民。有8749人家居檢疫，有144名在香港沒有居所的香港居民，在西貢戶外康樂中心及曹公潭戶外康樂中心進行檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265099&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1265099%26csid%3D261_341&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=2abde4d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1265099&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}